  "title": "Dental Assistant",
  "description": "<p><strong>✨ Hiring: Dental Assistant ✨</strong><br /></p><p><u>Responsibilities:</u></p><ul><li>Assist dentists during dental treatments and procedures</li><li>Prepare, sterilise, and maintain dental instruments in accordance with infection control standards</li><li>Provide chairside support and ensure patient comfort</li><li>Maintain cleanliness and infection control standards in the clinic</li></ul><p><u>Requirements:</u></p><ul><li>Minimum 1 year of experience as a Dental Assistant </li><li>Good communication and interpersonal skills</li><li>Responsible, attentive to detail, and patient-focused</li><li>Ability to multitask and work in a fast-paced environment</li><li>Willingness to learn and grow with the team</li></ul><p><u>What We Offer:</u></p><ul><li>Competitive salary package</li><li>On the job training and guidance provided</li></ul><p>📍 Location: Clementi/ West Coast area</p><p>🕒 Working Hours: 44 hours per week, 5 days (4 days weekday + 1 day weekend)</p>",
